lie
Discworld player help
lie

.SH Name
.SI 5
lie - Change your position to lying down.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
lie
lie on the floor
lie on <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Allows you to change your position.  To lie on the floor, or to lie on
something, or to just lie down if you are sitting.
.EP


.SH Examples
.SI 5
> lie
You lie down.
> lie on the floor
You lie on the floor.
> lie on table
You lie on the table.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
sit, stand, kneel, meditate, crouch
.EP
